Cookies vs JWT's

Cookies 
    * Transport mechanism 
    * Moves any kind of data between browser and server. 
    * Automatically managed by the browser. 

JWT's 
    * Authentication/ Authorization mechanism. 
    * Stores any data we want. 
    * We have to manage it manually. 